<h3>How to work with button groups</h3>
<h5 class="ms-5">A basic button group</h5>
<div class="btn-group ms-5 mb-3" role="group" aria-label="Button group">
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Home</a>
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Cart</a>
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Products</a>
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Contact Us</a>
</div>
<h5 class="ms-5">A toolbar with two buttons</h5>
<div class="btn-toolbar ms-5 mb-5" role="toolbar" aria-label="Toolbar with groups">
    <div class="btn-group me-2" role="group" aria-label="First group">
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Home</a>
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Cart</a>
    </div>
    <div asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" role="group" aria-label="Second group">
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Products</a>
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-info">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
</div>
<br />
<h3>How to work with badges and icons</h3>
<h5 class="ms-5">A button group that includes icons for both of its buttons</h5>
<div class="btn-group ms-5 mb-3" role="group" aria-label="Button group">
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="bi bi-house"></i></i>&nbsp;Home&nbsp;</a>
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="bi bi-cart4"></i>&nbsp;Cart&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<h5 class="ms-5">A button with a badge</h5>
<div class="ms-5 mb-3">
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary">&nbsp;Cart&nbsp;<span class="badge bg-primary">2</span></a>
</div>
<h5>A button with an icon and a badge</h5>
<div class="ms-5 mb-3">
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="bi bi-cart4"></i>&nbsp;Cart&nbsp<span class="badge bg-primary">2</span></a>
</div>
